UpdateCnameFlattening.title: UpdateCnameFlattening
UpdateCnameFlattening.summary: Modifies the CNAME flattening configuration of a website.

UpdateCrossBorderOptimization.title: UpdateCrossBorderOptimization
UpdateCrossBorderOptimization.summary: Modifies the configuration of the Chinese mainland network access optimization.

UpdateCustomScenePolicy.title: UpdateCustomScenePolicy
UpdateCustomScenePolicy.summary: Modifies the configurations of a custom scenario-specific policy.

UpdateDevelopmentMode.title: UpdateDevelopmentMode
UpdateDevelopmentMode.summary: Modifies the development mode configuration of your website. If you enable Development Mode, all requests bypass caching components on POPs and are redirected to the origin server. This allows clients to retrieve the most recent resources on the origin server.

UpdateEdgeContainerAppLogRiver.title: UpdateEdgeContainerAppLogRiver
UpdateEdgeContainerAppLogRiver.summary: Updates the log collection configuration of a containerized application.

UpdateEdgeContainerAppResourceReserve.title: UpdateEdgeContainerAppResourceReserve
UpdateEdgeContainerAppResourceReserve.summary: Updates the resource reservation configuration of an edge container.

UpdateHttpIncomingRequestHeaderModificat.title: UpdateHttpIncomingRequestHeaderModificationRule
UpdateHttpIncomingRequestHeaderModificat.summary: Updates the HTTP incoming request header modification rule.

UpdateHttpIncomingResponseHeaderModifica.title: UpdateHttpIncomingResponseHeaderModificationRule
UpdateHttpIncomingResponseHeaderModifica.summary: Updates the configuration of modifying HTTP response headers for a website.

UpdateIPv6.title: UpdateIPv6
UpdateIPv6.summary: Modifies the IPv6 configuration of a website.

UpdateManagedTransform.title: UpdateManagedTransform
UpdateManagedTransform.summary: Modifies the configuration of managed transforms for your website.

UpdateOriginProtectionIpWhiteList.title: UpdateOriginProtectionIpWhiteList
UpdateOriginProtectionIpWhiteList.summary: Updates the IP whitelist for origin protection used by a website to the latest version.

UpdateOriginRule.title: Modify Origin Rule Configuration for Site
UpdateOriginRule.summary: Modify Origin Rule Configuration for Site

UpdatePage.title: UpdatePage
UpdatePage.summary: Modifies the configurations of a custom error page, such as the name, description, content type, and content of the page.

UpdateRecord.title: UpdateRecord
UpdateRecord.summary: Updates multiple types of DNS records and origin authentication configurations.

UpdateRoutineConfigDescription.title: UpdateRoutineConfigDescription
UpdateRoutineConfigDescription.summary: Modifies the description of a routine.

UpdateRoutineRoute.title: UpdateRoutineRoute
UpdateRoutineRoute.summary: Modifies the route configuration of an edge function.

UpdateScheduledPreloadExecution.title: UpdateScheduledPreloadExecution
UpdateScheduledPreloadExecution.summary: Updates a scheduled prefetch plan based on the plan ID.

UpdateSeoBypass.title: UpdateSeoBypass
UpdateSeoBypass.summary: Modifies the search engine crawler configuration for a website.

UpdateSiteAccessType.title: UpdateSiteAccessType
UpdateSiteAccessType.summary: Converts the DNS setup option of a website.

UpdateSiteCoverage.title: UpdateSiteCoverage
UpdateSiteCoverage.summary: Modifies the service location for a single website. This updates the acceleration configuration of the website to adapt to changes in traffic distribution, and improve user experience in specific regions.

UpdateSiteCustomLog.title: UpdateSiteCustomLog
UpdateSiteCustomLog.summary: Modifies the configuration of custom request header, response header, and cookie fields that are used to capture logs of a website.

UpdateSiteDeliveryTask.title: UpdateSiteDeliveryTask
UpdateSiteDeliveryTask.summary: Modifies a real-time log delivery task.

UpdateSiteDeliveryTaskStatus.title: UpdateSiteDeliveryTaskStatus
UpdateSiteDeliveryTaskStatus.summary: Changes the status of a real-time log delivery task.

UpdateSiteNameExclusive.title: UpdateSiteNameExclusive
UpdateSiteNameExclusive.summary: Modifies the site hold configuration of a website. After you enable site hold, other accounts cannot add your website domain or its subdomains to ESA.

UpdateSitePause.title: UpdateSitePause
UpdateSitePause.summary: Modifies the ESA proxy configuration of a website.

UpdateSiteVanityNS.title: UpdateSiteVanityNS
UpdateSiteVanityNS.summary: Updates the custom nameserver names for a single website.

UpdateTieredCache.title: UpdateTieredCache
UpdateTieredCache.summary: Modifies the tiered cache configuration of your website.

UpdateUserDeliveryTask.title: UpdateUserDeliveryTask
UpdateUserDeliveryTask.summary: Modifies the configurations of a delivery task, including the task name, log field, log category, and discard rate.

UpdateUserDeliveryTaskStatus.title: UpdateUserDeliveryTaskStatus
UpdateUserDeliveryTaskStatus.summary: Changes the status of a delivery task in your Alibaba Cloud account.

UpdateVideoProcessing.title: UpdateVideoProcessing
UpdateVideoProcessing.summary: Modifies the video processing configuration of the site.

UpdateWaitingRoom.title: UpdateWaitingRoom
UpdateWaitingRoom.summary: Modifies the configurations of a waiting room.

UpdateWaitingRoomEvent.title: UpdateWaitingRoomEvent
UpdateWaitingRoomEvent.summary: Modifies the configurations of a waiting room event.

UploadClientCaCertificate.title: UploadClientCaCertificate
UploadClientCaCertificate.summary: Uploads a client certificate authority (CA) certificate.

UploadFile.title: UploadFile
UploadFile.summary: Uploads the file that contains resources to be purged or prefetched.

VerifySite.title: VerifySite
VerifySite.summary: Verifies the ownership of a website domain. Websites that pass the verification are automatically activated.
